com.brtbeacon.sdk

类 BRTBeacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brtbeacon.sdk.BRTBeacon

  • public class BRTBeacon
extends java.lang.Object
     Immutable representations of single beacon.
 Two beacons are considered equal if their proximity UUID, major and minor and macaddress are equal.
